    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style! This fantastic vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for your next set of wheels. It's clean, runs smoothly, and shows only minor signs of careful use, ensuring it's ready for many more miles of adventure. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that looks great and performs even better, this is the one for you!",
