    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all essential mechanical systems are in solid working order. While there may be minor signs of regular use, it is a reliable driver that is ready for the road without any immediate major repairs needed.",
