      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, representing the pinnacle of its class. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, presenting in showroom condition with no discernible wear. Every surface reflects a commitment to excellence, and its mechanical performance remains unrivaled. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering provides a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of significant pedigree and flawless presentation.",
      "price": 48250.0,
